# Malik Al Waqt

## Vision
A luxury shopping app for premium watches and branded perfumes.

## Owner
Muhammad Salman

## Target Platform
- Android
- Google Play Store

## Categories
- Luxury Watches
- Premium Perfumes

## Features
- User Login & Signup
- Product Search
- Wishlist
- Shopping Cart
- Secure Checkout
- Order Tracking
- User Profile
- Push Notifications

## Admin Features
- Add/Edit/Delete Products
- Manage Orders
- Manage Users
- Sales Dashboard
- Coupon Management

## Technology (Final Target)
Frontend: Flutter
Backend: Node.js
Database: PostgreSQL
Notifications: Firebase Cloud Messaging


